        <body>
            <div type="bibliography">
                
            </div>
            <div type="edition" xml:lang="gez">
                <div type="textpart" xml:id="exhortationprayer">
                    <note>The following text is taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/RDW009">Hamburg, Asien-Afrika-Institut, Fund RDW-009</ref>.</note>
                    <ab>በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ፩፡ አምላክ፡ ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ዓይነ፡ ጥላ፡ ወመደንግጸ፡ አጋንንት፡ ወመደንግጸ፡ ሰይጣናት፡</ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" xml:id="masgabiya">
                    <note>The following text is taken from <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/BL5NWGBV"><seg type="webpage"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:MgWebsite"/><title level="a">መልክአ፡ ጉባኤ፡ Malkǝʾa gubāʾe</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Augustine</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Dickinson</t:surname></author><date>2020</date><note type="accessed">2024-09-24</note><note type="url">https://malkeagubae.com/</note></bibl>.</note>
                    <lg type="stanza" n="1">
                        <l n="1">ሰላም፡ ለተፈጥሮትከ፡ ምስለ፡ መላእክት፡ ኅቡረ፨</l>
                        <l n="2">እንዘ፡ ኢትከውን፡ ቅድመ፡ ወእንዘ፡ ኢትዴኀር፡ ድኅረ፨</l>
                        <l n="3">ሰዳዴ፡ ሰይጣናት፡ ፋኑኤል፡ እምላዕለ፡ ሰብእ፡ ወትረ፨</l>
                        <l n="4">ስድዶሙ፡ ለአጋንንት፡ ወአርእዮሙ፡ ኀሳረ፨</l>
                        <l n="5">ከመ፡ ኢይግበሩ፡ ኪያየ፡ ማኅደረ፨</l>
                    </lg>
                </div>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text></TEI>